\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16209235 During the past four weeks concern at the behaviour of young people has continued widespread. Complaints have been chiefly of:
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid9123155 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9123155 
